/**
 * Campaign Management Component
 * 
 * TOKEN-BASED AUTHENTICATION SYSTEM:
 * - Uses token format: userId-username-role-mallId-shopId-timestamp
 * - Example: "12-sandra-shop_admin-6-6-1763753837104"
 * - All operations use authenticated mall_id and shop_id from token
 * - Eliminates hardcoded usernames and complex permission arrays
 * 
 * Key Functions:
 * - parseAuthToken(): Extracts user data from token
 * - getCurrentUserMallAndShop(): Token-driven user identification
 * - All API calls use authenticated shop_id from token
 * - Debug logging throughout for tracking authentication
 */

